channel.title: Maintenance Info
channel.description:
Im going to use this post to let users know of any 'maintenance information' regarding the community library. The aim is of course not to impact users, so its just informational.
PM me if you need any more info, or see anything 'unexpected'
Information ==== 11-07-2016 : merge changes from master (1.0.9) to 1.0.10
Users are reminded, they should now be using either 1.0.6 (release) or 1.0.10 (latest test version) If you are on any other version, and in particular prior tests (1.0.7 to 1.0.9) please upgrade.
